plot: Shannon's 60th birthday extravaganza continues, but the mood is anything but celebratory when Tamra and Shannon continue their friendship war. The ladies hop on a double-decker bus tour where Gina questions Heather about another issue in their friendship and Jenn finds out there is gossip surrounding her financial decisions. When secret texts are exposed that allege Tamra dug up dirt on Ryan, Jenn confronts Tamra in an explosive showdown.
